data.description: Back yard retreat w/red pavers create a warm and inviting patio, perfect for relaxing or entertaining. Mature greenery provides shade and privacy, creating a tranquil atmosphere. A small shed offers additional storage space for gardening tools or outdoor gear. There is more storage space in the 2 car garage for all your belongings. This charming home features two living areas, providing plenty of space for relaxing or gathering with loved ones. If you need an extra bedroom the back area can be used as a bedroom or office. You don't have to worry about raking the Fall leaves-the HOA takes care of the front yard. Close to UNM Regional Med Center, Hewlett Packard and RR Event Center. Sold as is.This home is sure to impress!
